This paper deals with efficient aggregation queries on large datasets, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of quantile sketches also involves statistical methods and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the use of a cascade, which is a technique commonly used in signal processing and information theory (cs.SI).
